comments: If you understand the concepts and work hard on the homework, then you probably won\'t have to complete the final.

Great Professor, funny guy, he\'s a programmer at heart, very tech savvy, has his own youtube channel and online courseworkbook available for free to students and non-students alike. Very responsive via email or comments on BitBucket repositories. Also a gamer, uses examples from games like EVE Online. 1010 would take again.
Great teacher!! He knows how to make "school" fun.
Pretty funny guy! You will look forward to going to class everyday!
Very knowledgable of the real world. He\'s a total computer geek but what can you expect. Funny guy with many witty and nerdy remarks.
